  "notes": [
    {
      "id": "note1",
      "position": {"x": 100, "y": 50},
      "text": "FARMASSIST+ HORIZONTAL FARM KIT (H1)\nTarget Farms: Bafang (Cacao), Bertoua (Cassava), Maroua (Groundnut)\nMCU: ESP32-DevKitC-32E\nArchitecture: Bun + Hono + Prisma + MQTT\nGCD4F 2026 Competition"
    },
    {
      "id": "note2",
      "position": {"x": 100, "y": 550},
      "text": "POWER NOTES:\n- Main: 12V 5A AC/DC adapter\n- Buck converter adjusted to 5V for ESP32 and relay module\n- 3.3V sourced from ESP32 onboard regulator\n- Total current draw: ~2.5A @ 12V"
    },
    {
      "id": "note3",
      "position": {"x": 400, "y": 550},
      "text": "I2C BUS:\n- SDA: GPIO21 (with 4.7K pull-up to 3.3V)\n- SCL: GPIO22 (with 4.7K pull-up to 3.3V)\n- Devices: BH1750 (0x23)\n- Can add more I2C sensors to same bus"
    },
    {
      "id": "note4",
      "position": {"x": 700, "y": 550},
      "text": "MQTT TOPICS:\nPublish: farmassist/{user_id}/{farm_id}/ARD_H001_001/telemetry\nSubscribe: farmassist/{user_id}/{farm_id}/ARD_H001_001/cmd\nBroker: localhost:1883 (dev) or :8883 (prod TLS)\nPublish Interval: 30 seconds"
    },
    {
      "id": "note5",
      "position": {"x": 200, "y": 550},
      "text": "CALIBRATION REQUIRED:\n- Soil Moisture: Dry vs Saturated\n- Soil pH: pH 4.0, 7.0, 9.0 buffers\n- DHT22: Factory calibrated\n- BH1750: Factory calibrated"
    },
    {
      "id": "note6",
      "position": {"x": 600, "y": 550},
      "text": "RS485 MODBUS:\n- Baud Rate: 9600\n- Data Bits: 8\n- Parity: None\n- Stop Bits: 1\n- NPK Sensor Address: 0x01 (default)\n- Enable GPIO18 high before TX"
    }
  ],
  "metadata": {
    "total_components": 12,
    "estimated_cost_xaf": 33700,
    "estimated_cost_usd": 55,
    "power_consumption": "30W max",
    "operating_temp": "-10 to 60°C",
    "pcb_size": "150mm x 100mm",
    "enclosure": "IP54 rated plastic box"
  }
}
